data.description: Sitting pretty on a 1.44 acre lot, this modern farmhouse offers the perfect blend of country living just minutes from all the modern conveniences of town. Guests are welcomed by an inviting rocking chair front porch and grand 2-story entrance foyer. A huge great room is centered around a masonry fireplace and hearth with a lovely mantle. Fabulous transoms and floor to ceiling windows flood the interior with natural light. The dining room is accented with wainscoting and pretty lighting. A sunny kitchen offers tons of solid wood cabinets, gorgeous granite countertops and a bay window overlooking the backyard oasis. Separate laundry with storage cabinets, mud sink and pantry. Pinterest inspired guest bath with tile flooring and solid surface counters. A spacious main floor owner's suite has a walk-in closet and beautifully remodeled ensuite bath with dual vanities, custom cabinetry, garden tub, walk-in tiled shower and flooring set on point. Two additional generous bedrooms with ample walk-in closets are served by a jack-n-jill bath. Other features: hardwoods and crown molding in main living areas, breakfast room, wood burning fireplace, large walk-in attic, screened porch, deck, black vinyl coated fenced yard, 22X12 above ground pool, heavy duty 41X18 RV shed, heated/cooled 2-car side entry garage with new wifi operated garage door, new interior & exterior paint. Don't miss this rare find with no HOA located just 5 miles from I-20's exit 1. Convenient to shopping, dining and medical facilities. Qualifies for 100% USDA financing and no city taxes!
